God has blessed us to be a blessing — and that’s what we did this week through @elevationoutreach and LOVE Week. 

Thank you to everyone who served the cities where God has positioned us to be His church.

We’re grateful for all of our outreach partners. What an awesome tradition. Thank you for being that kind of church @elevationchurch. #LW21
